document_data.name: Ostel
document_data.mainbody: The '''Barony of Ostel''' was one of the physically smaller provinces of [[Damara]] in [[1357 DR]].
document_data.Geography: Ostel sat within central Damara. Its entire eastern border was bordered by the waters of the [[Goliad River]], [[Lake Mogador]], and the [[Great Imphras River]]. [[Impiltur]] bordered Ostel to the south.
document_data.Description: Rich farmlard dominated much of Ostel's countryside, thanks to the major rivers flowing through the barony.
document_data.History:
Members of the [[Praka family]] were the traditional rulers of Ostel, with Baroness [[Sylvia Praka|Sylvia]] representing the family as of 1357 DR. Sylvia was the 23rd member of her family to rule Ostel.

Ostel boasted the largest population of any province in Damara before [[Morov]] and [[Heliogabalus]] combined.
document_data.Activities: As a direct appointment of [[Zhengyi]], Sylvia was hated by most of her subjects.
